meta.title: I Meet Timothy The Bear*DO NOT EDIT*-Roger

bubble.text: Ignore the gray sidewalk set. i only this possible part of the forest(Sort of)

ttsdata.text: Well, It is a nice warming day out here in these woods. I kinda want to go and play with my friends
It's only a chance if i run into 1 of them at least
Hello there. Are you wanting something from me?
Honestly no, but, you kinda remind me of another bear i met back in 2020
Yeah, Back then i met 1 who had a jar of honey
Well yes, We bears do like honey sometimes
I see. Is this your forest?
You could say that. This forest is pretty nice, as well as the warmness is it out here. And oh, What you're looking at is the possible part of this forest
Odd, but ok. What's your name by the way? I'm roger
I'm timothy, timothy the bear. Nice to meet you. You're that guy who has a friend named kimberly
Well, Yeah, That's me. I've been her friend for so long i don't know what will happen next with me and her, but hopefully it's nothing bad with me and her
